node.text:
COHIBA LANCEROS 2000 💨🇨🇺
Continuing my 55k followers celebration with a cigar that started everything for @habanos_oficial COHIBA brand 55 years ago… 
Love the coincidence that we have number 55 at the same time! 
And @stdupont is here to add some spice to it with amazing Cohiba Le Grand 55 Aniversario 🔥💪🏻🇨🇺💨
Life is good!!! 
Enjoy it & thx one more time for amazing support 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻
